{"tid":1977510,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"浪費人生一流系列！自製梅菜扣肉！","createTime":"2020-04-18T04:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T07:35:21.000Z","uid":68594,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b444921a55cc8142e4ffef6fe5dadd144e8eeeb","tid":1977510,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"大家好啊！我係子言張！<br />\n今次唔係教我老婆煮飯，因為疫情太得閒嘅關係，Send CV出去又沒回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我決定整啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「可一不可再」</span></span>嘅菜式出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">梅菜扣肉！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實材料真係唔難，但係製造嘅時間真係長到阿媽都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趁大家仲係疫情要留係屋企，有興趣嘅朋友，又想浪費下人生時間，可以試吓整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ygp3aQMLvVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYgp3aQMLvVE&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppevFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=19c24ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ygp3aQMLvVE</a>"},{"pid":"6ec567efc34c2abc07430b8d08877a940be8c136","tid":1977510,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"推 樓主有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fea7793132903ba85ad17f641991f815a8e7a6","tid":1977510,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"已subscribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b523f97333ee67231ca1019cf06797858da6156","tid":1977510,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"其實扣肉是咪一定要搭梅菜<br />\n我鍾意食扣肉,但梅菜就不了"},{"pid":"570ca882a26dc5eaeb41bcba1e9f6dede5adc154","tid":1977510,"uid":259532,"like":0,"d